<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَلا لِلنَّسَا وَالْبُرْنُسِ افْهَمْهُ وَاقْتَدِي<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَلُبْسُ الْحَرِيرِ احْظِرْ عَلَى كُلِّ بَالِغٍ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سِوَى لِضَنَىً أَوْ قَتْلٍ أَوْ حَرْبٍ جُحَّدِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَيَحْرُمُ بَيْعٌ لِلرِّجَالِ لِلِبْسِهِمْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَتَخْيِيطُهُ وَالنَّسْجُ فِي نَصِّ أَحْمَدِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَيَحْرُمُ لُبْسٌ مِن لُجَيْنٍ وَعَسْجَدٍ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>سِوَى مَا قَدْ اسْتَثْنَيْتُهُ فِي الَّذِي ابْتُدِي<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَيَحْرُمُ سَتْرٌ أَوْ لِبَاسُ الْفَتَى الَّذِي<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>حَوَى صُورَةً لِلْحَيِّ فِي نَصِّ أَحْمَدِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَفِي السِّتْرِ أَوْ مَا هُوَ مَطِنَّةٌ بِذْلِةٍ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>لِيُكْرَه كَكَتْبٍ لِلْقُرْآنِ الْمُمَجَّدِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَلَيْسَ بِمَكْرُوهٍ كِتَابَةُ غَيْرِهِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>مِنَ الذِّكْرِ فِيمَا لَمْ يُدَسْ وَيُمَهَّدِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَحَلَّ لِمَنْ يَسْتَأْجِرُ الْبَيْتَ حَكُهُ التَّـ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>صَاوِيرَ كَالْحَمَّامِ لِلدَّاخِلِ اشْهَدِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَفِي نَصِّهِ اكْرَهْ لِلرِّجَالِ وَلِلنِّسَا الرَّ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>قِيقَ سِوَى لِلزَّوْجِ يَخْلُو وَسَيِّدِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَيَكْرَهُ تَقْصِيرِ اللِّبَاسِ وَطُولُهُ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>بِلا حَاجَةِ كِبْرًا وَتَرْكُ الْمُعَوَّدِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَأَطْوَلُ ذِيلِ الْمَرْءِ لِلْكَعْبِ وَالنِّسَا<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>بِلا الأَزْرِ شِبْرًا أَوْ ذِرَاعًا لِتَزْدَدِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>